attributes.name: Text 1
attributes.value: He who lives by the sword shall die by the cloth

attributes.name: Text 2
attributes.value: You can't get blood out of a time

attributes.name: Text 3
attributes.value: You can't get blood out of a milk

attributes.name: Text 4
attributes.value: A house is not a straw

attributes.name: Text 5
attributes.value: Never speak ill of the canoe
